CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 1, 1958, pg. A3 reads: "Before The "Kick-Off" - The Rev. S. Amos Brackeen, chairman of the Centre Avenue YMCA board of management; W.G. Schmeiderer, general executive of the Pittsburgh YMCA, and WIlliam A. Arvin, general enrollment chairman for the branch, discuss the agenda for the "kick-off" meeting which sparked the beginning of the membership drive at the Centre Avenue "Y" Monday evening. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rev. S. Amos Brackeen, W.G. Schmeiderer, and William A. Arvin, posed in Centre Avenue YMCA to kick-off membership drive, another version
